4800 W Old Bingham Hwy is a light rail station in the Welby neighborhood of West Jordan, Utah, in the United States, served by the Red Line of the Utah Transit Authority's (UTA) TRAX light rail system. The Red Line provides service from the University of Utah to the Daybreak Community of South Jordan.


== Description ==
The station is located at 4773 West Old Bingham Highway and is easily accessible from Old Bingham Highway.
